[Schedule]
day month weekday
x x * # every weekday
* x x # every day
* 10,11 x # day 1 of every October and November (defaults to day 1)
2-5 3/5 x # days 2-5, every fifth month from March


[Except]
minute hour day month weekday
1-15 * * * * # not at 1-15 minutes past every hour, every day
1-59 * * * 7,0 # not at 1-15 minutes past every hour, every Saturday and Sunday
* 9-17 * * 1-6 # not between 9.00 and 17.00 every Monday to Friday

